data.description: Seller offering credits!! Welcome to your dream riverfront retreat! Come find yourself on over an acre, surrounded by the soothing sounds of the river in a private cul-de-sac, where you'll relish the sense of security and peace that this location offers. This stunning 3-4 bedroom, 2 bathroom ranch home is a masterpiece of modern living and comfort set against the backdrop of nature's finest. As you enter, a curving driveway welcomes you to this oasis, offering breathtaking 180-degree panoramic views that will leave you in awe. The exterior of the house, meticulously maintained and freshly painted, boasts impeccable curb appeal, setting the stage for the comfort that awaits inside. Step out onto the vast, inviting patio with its accompanying spa, providing the perfect spot to unwind and take in the picturesque views. Multi-level decking adds to the outdoor charm, offering multiple areas for relaxation, entertaining, dining and more!
